title: wati - not dead
seo_description: It is Easter period, the total reminder of the fact that we are not serving a dead God. The beautiful singer Wati, uses her amazing voice to bring light to our advantage in Christ. God's not dead, He is alive and for ever present with us.
description: It is Easter period, the total reminder of the fact that we are not serving a dead God. The beautiful singer Wati, uses her amazing voice to bring light to our advantage in Christ. God's not dead, He is alive and for ever present with us. Dwells among us and takes care of us.
